data.title: Winschoterdiep 50 Groningen
data.text:
Winschoterdiep 50

This recently developed office building is located in the Europark. Europark is known as a young and up-coming environment. The property has a large garden and a luxurious brasserie for lunches and fresh coffee. A variety of restaurants, sports centers, and supermarkets can be found in the immediate vicinity.

Rental rates

Office spaces can be rented in this office building from 15m2 up to 15,765m2! if interested, we would like to inform you about the prices here.

MyMeeting and MyCanteen

If you are a tenant within this office concept, you can use closed rooms for meetings, events, and other gatherings. There is also a luxury brasserie for daily fresh coffee, lunches, and drinks.

Location and accessibility

The property is located at the Europapark in Groningen. The accessibility of this office building is excellent. You can easily reach the office by car from the southern ring road or the Europaweg. The office building is also easily accessible by public transport. For example, the new Europapark train station is within walking distance and there is a good bus connection. The building has approximately 358 parking spaces and is on-site.
